<br>
The other problem is that the conclusion you seemed to have drawm from my premise was different than the one I drew.  I merely said that it would be better to have a warrior tank the boss.  I didn't say that that automatically made up for being less useful on the previous waves.  The purpose was to illustrate that each class is a useful tank, just in different ways.  Ideally, you'd have an SK do the waves and then you'd switch to a warrior for the boss.  Most groups don't have the luxury to take two tanks, though.<br>
